  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Manager</h2>The Manager is the office's ultimate authority figure, tasked with ensuring productivity and firing the Slackers hiding among the Specialists.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/c2f95b4d8d0a4fc3c63158f7cd0cdee9.poster.avif?t=1738015624\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/c2f95b4d8d0a4fc3c63158f7cd0cdee9.webm?t=1738015624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/c2f95b4d8d0a4fc3c63158f7cd0cdee9.mp4?t=1738015624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slackers</h2>The Slacker's goal is to goof off without getting caught. Whether it’s playing Minesweeper, or taking a dump, Slackers must blend in to avoid the Manager’s wrath.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/3fc876a6216019ebf52c625feaae722a.poster.avif?t=1738015624\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/3fc876a6216019ebf52c625feaae722a.webm?t=1738015624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/3fc876a6216019ebf52c625feaae722a.mp4?t=1738015624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Specialists</h2>Specialists are the backbone of the company, assigned various tasks that keep the office running smoothly. But even the hardest workers know that productivity sometimes requires a coffee break.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/c34cfa7aa86fddb63daf0b78e9181ab1.poster.avif?t=1738015624\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/c34cfa7aa86fddb63daf0b78e9181ab1.webm?t=1738015624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/c34cfa7aa86fddb63daf0b78e9181ab1.mp4?t=1738015624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Mechanics</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Objective-Based Gameplay: Specialists are tasked with completing objectives to contribute to the company's success, whereas Slackers engage in activities to appear busy while avoiding actual work.<br></li><li>Social Deduction and Strategy: Players utilize proximity voice chat for real-time discussions, alliances, and accusations, making social interactions crucial to gameplay.<br></li><li>Managerial Oversight: The Manager must observe, deduce, and decide who to fire, with each choice potentially altering the game's balance.<br>Experience the Office Like Never Before:</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Manager</h2>The Manager is the office's ultimate authority figure, tasked with ensuring productivity and firing the Slackers hiding among the Specialists.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/c2f95b4d8d0a4fc3c63158f7cd0cdee9.poster.avif?t=1738015624\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/c2f95b4d8d0a4fc3c63158f7cd0cdee9.webm?t=1738015624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/c2f95b4d8d0a4fc3c63158f7cd0cdee9.mp4?t=1738015624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slackers</h2>The Slacker's goal is to goof off without getting caught. Whether it’s playing Minesweeper, or taking a dump, Slackers must blend in to avoid the Manager’s wrath.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/3fc876a6216019ebf52c625feaae722a.poster.avif?t=1738015624\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/3fc876a6216019ebf52c625feaae722a.webm?t=1738015624\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920570/extras/3fc876a6216019ebf52c625feaae722a.mp4?t=1738015624\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Specialists</h2>Specialists are the backbone of the company, assigned various tasks that keep the office running smoothly. But even the hardest workers know that productivity sometimes requires a coffee break.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamst